= Recommendation =

Based on the preceding sections and analysis, it is strongly recommended to learn more about GNU/Linux and install a suitable distribution although at a severe security decrease. Otherwise, significant effort is required to play "whack-a-mole" with Windows, which routinely subjects users to surveillance and freedom restrictions.

